      "value": "Borrego Springs Unified is a small K-12 rural district serving 614 students with active IEPs, including 15 autistic students. All 15 autistic students and the entire SWD population are reported to spend 80% or more of the school day in general-education settings, with no students in fully separate special-education placements."
